image_analysis.description: A photograph of a small bathroom or powder room. The room features a white toilet, patterned wallpaper with vertical stripes and a diamond/checkerboard motif, and a dark-framed piece of art on the right wall. A large, dark-colored gorilla head sculpture is mounted on the wall above the toilet. A small bottle with a pump dispenser sits on the back of the toilet tank. The photo is taken from a doorway, with the door frame visible on the left and right edges.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a small room, portrait orientation.

notes: The image is a photograph included in a document set, identified by the Bates stamp EFTA00000061.
